WEBVTT

00:04:28.600 --> 00:04:30.196
hours for hours,

00:04:30.196 --> 00:04:31.908
and then their mothers came,

00:04:31.908 --> 00:04:35.642
and they are beating in this position,

00:04:35.642 --> 00:04:40.258
for hours, giving water and beating.

00:04:40.258 --> 00:04:41.886
And then the polishers come.

00:04:41.886 --> 00:04:46.944
They start polishing it with a stone for hours.

00:04:46.944 --> 00:04:51.901
And then you have this result,

00:04:51.901 --> 00:04:55.210
very fine, like a baby bottom.

00:04:55.210 --> 00:04:56.983
(Laughter)

00:04:56.983 --> 00:05:02.248
It's not photoshopped. (Laughter)